Name: The spy who shot me™
About the game: The spy who shot me™ is a comedy arcade-like FPS. Served up in a 90's retro style. Take the roll of super spy Agent7! As he fights against the evil S.C.U.M. *********************************************************************************** Features -> Arcade style fast gameplay, -> Traditional Retro Army humor, -> Hordes of enemies to combat, -> Unique run and gun gameplay, -> Vehicle action, -> Weapon Mods, -> Lovely pointy polygons, *********************************************************************************** 'There you are! I've been waiting... I want you to test out this new software we've developed. It's top secret mind you' - Mother
